        "created_at": "2025-12-18T20:02:29.409Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The media gallery feature in Signal Desktop recently underwent a major redesign, allowing you to view media, files, audio, and links all in one place. However, it does not include a search function to look through the media history of a specific conversation.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/2/a/2a48daffb21bbeabef5496c89bbe6f3fcc528d9b.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/2a48daffb21bbeabef5496c89bbe6f3fcc528d9b\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/a/2a48daffb21bbeabef5496c89bbe6f3fcc528d9b_2_672x500.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"62492J6gmdWCYJX5Rbb2WxaeffJ\" width=\"672\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/a/2a48daffb21bbeabef5496c89bbe6f3fcc528d9b_2_672x500.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/a/2a48daffb21bbeabef5496c89bbe6f3fcc528d9b_2_1008x750.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/a/2a48daffb21bbeabef5496c89bbe6f3fcc528d9b_2_1344x1000.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"131313\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">2500Ã—1858 115 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Of course, there is a search bar in the top left corner of the window, but it is counterintuitive because it lacks categorizations, titles, and thumbnails compared to the new media gallery.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/8/f/8f3ba6422baafd85d295c7285a2610d040bf8043.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/8f3ba6422baafd85d295c7285a2610d040bf8043\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/8/f/8f3ba6422baafd85d295c7285a2610d040bf8043.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"kr64KxYIzXKq8IyDQGIafnYsZTZ\" width=\"538\" height=\"246\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">538Ã—246 4.23 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>I would like to kindly request a feature: please add a search button to the top right of the media gallery. This button would allow users to easily search for images, videos, files, audio, and links within a specific chat, displaying results with thumbnails and titles.</p>",
